<p>Teamwork Commerce is proud to support our community by donating backpacks to five local Title 1 schools in Pinellas County, just in time for the first day of school on August 12. Each school, Eisenhower Elementary, Skycrest Elementary, Belcher Elementary, Sandy Lane Elementary, and Oak Grove Middle School, received five boxes of Teamwork Commerce backpacks, totaling 125 backpacks, to help students start the school year with the supplies they need.</p>

<h2>Giving back to Clearwater</h2>
<p>We're committed to giving back to the Clearwater area and helping make sure local students are prepared for a successful academic year.</p>
